---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — PhoneHub"
  description="PhoneHub privacy policy. Learn how we handle your data and what information we collect."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At PhoneHub, your privacy is important to us. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what choices you have.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">PhoneHub is designed to work without requiring you to create an account or provide personal information. Specifically:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">No personal data collection</strong> — We do not require registration, and we do not collect your name, email address, phone number, or other personal identifiers.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Usage analytics</strong> — We may use privacy-respecting analytics (such as page view counts) to understand how the site is used and improve the experience. This data is aggregated and does not identify individual users.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          PhoneHub may use cookies or local storage to remember your preferences (such as theme or recently viewed products). These cookies are strictly functional and do not track you across other websites. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time without affecting the core functionality of the site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our site contains affiliate links to retailers such as Amazon, Flipkart, and other partners. When you click on these links, the retailer may place tracking cookies on your device to attribute the referral. This tracking is governed by the respective retailer's privacy policy, not ours. We may earn a small commission from qualifying purchases at no additional cost to you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">PhoneHub uses third-party services to deliver content and functionality:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Image CDNs</strong> — Product images are served from third-party CDNs (GSMArena, Wikimedia Commons, etc.). These services may log your IP address when serving images.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Google Fonts</strong> — We use Google Fonts for typography, which may collect limited data as described in Google's privacy policy.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Hosting</strong> — PhoneHub is hosted on GitHub Pages. GitHub may collect technical data as described in their privacy statement.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          Since we do not collect personal data, there is minimal risk of data exposure. All connections to PhoneHub are served over HTTPS to encrypt data in transit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          PhoneHub is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us and we will take appropriate action.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of PhoneHub after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please visit our <a href="/phonehub/contact" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
